# 懵然不知
(pos:成語)
<explanation>
yue:完全唔知道發生咩事，對情況一無所知。
eng:to be completely unaware; to know nothing about something
<eg>
yue:佢成日瞓覺，對公司嘅變動懵然不知。 (keoi5 sing4 jat6 fan2 zoek3, doi3 gong1 sai1 dik1 bin3 dung6 mung4 jin4 bat1 zi1.)
eng:He is always sleeping and is completely unaware of the changes in the company. [end of text]


